  <name>Cube Timer</name>
  <summary>Rubik's Cube timer</summary>
	<description>
	  <p>
	    Cube Timer is a simple Rubik's Cube Timer application for the GNOME desktop.
	    Just long press the space-bar and start solving!
	  </p>
	  <p>Following puzzles are supported :- </p>
    <ul>
      <li>3x3x3</li>
      <li>2x2x2</li>
      <li>4x4x4</li>
      <li>5x5x5</li>
      <li>6x6x6</li>
      <li>7x7x7</li>
      <li>Skewb</li>
      <li>Megaminx</li>
      <li>Pyraminx</li>
      <li>Clock</li>
    </ul>
	</description>
