  <releases>
    <release version="0.2.0" date="2025-01-01">
      <description translate="no">
        <p>Happy New Year !!!</p>
        <p>This release adds some preferences and full screen support.</p>
        <p>Preferences added: </p>
        <ul>
          <li>Hold to start: Hold 'space' to start the timer</li>
          <li>Stop timer with any key</li>
          <li>WCA averages: best and worst solves are ignored while calculating averages</li>
          <li>Zen Mode: Hide all elements while solving</li>
          <li>Always show minutes</li>
          <li>Timer precision: number of digits after decimal point</li>
        </ul>
        <p>Translations update:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Brazilian Portuguese (Renato Tavares)</li>
        </ul>
        <p>This is also the first minor update: version 0.2</p>
        <p>Thank you for using the app!</p>
      </description>
    </release>
